      "transcript": {
        "text": {
          "en-AU": "Welcome to learning about animal habitats! A habitat is an animal's natural home where it can find food, water, shelter, and space to live. Different animals are specially adapted to live in different environments like deserts, rainforests, oceans, and grasslands. Let's explore how animals survive in their unique homes!"
        }
      },
